snippet: On a difficult, rain-soaked course, Eun-Hee Ji scrambled to a one-shot lead over Hall of Famer Karrie Webb in the L.P.G.A. Championship, with four players two strokes behind.
abstract: Eun-Hee Ji takes third-round lead at LPGA Championship, with four players two strokes behind.
lead_paragraph: On a difficult, rain-soaked course, Eun-Hee Ji scrambled to a one-shot lead over Hall of Famer Karrie Webb in the L.P.G.A. Championship, with four players two strokes behind.

headline.seo: Eun-Hee Ji Leads Karrie Webb by one in L.P.G.A.
headline.main: Tight Group Near Top in Soggy L.P.G.A. Championship
